name: MQ Game Jam 2
description:
Clumsy you spilled water all over your really old, really volatile computer causing it to explode violently. Fix your computer as quickly and as accurately as possible to get back to work.

You like spaghetti. Me too. Check out my spaghetti here: https://github.com/marksabamq/MQGameJam2

Game was made for Macquarie University's 2nd Game Jam.
